I"b<p>As from issue 15, authors contributing to <a href="https://journals.openedition.org/variants">Variants</a> can also submit their articles or reviews in LaTeX format. For some, this may mean a new way of working. At first sight, a LaTeX file looks rather daunting and indeed it takes some getting used to. Luckily there are many great introductions and handy templates to get you started. And there are userfriendly applications like <a href="https://overleaf.com">Overleaf</a> that will help you write and visualize LaTeX.</p>

